  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "The tasks are ordered by the number of samples (i.e., data points) in the task.",
    "There is a clear delineation in the leading algorithms based on the number of samples in the task.",
    "The MODNet algorithm 57 is the clear leader on tasks with <10,000 samples, leading 5 out of 7 tasks in this category.",
    "However, these particular tasks do not have a structure provided and only chemical composition is known.",
    "Meanwhile, for tasks with >10,000 samples, the (related) coNGN 58 and coGN 58 algorithms lead 5 out of 6 tasks."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Meanwhile, for tasks with >10,000 samples, the (related) coNGN 58 and coGN 58 algorithms lead 5 out of 6 tasks."
  ]
